comments: Simmons (PHI) makes marginal contact to Ball's (NOP) body during his shooting motion on the driving shot attempt.
Johnson (NOP) swipes down and makes contact with Embiid's (PHI) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Green (PHI) makes incidental contact to Hernangomez's (NOP) arm after the release of his shot attempt.
Bledsoe (NOP) makes marginal contact with Embiid's (PHI) arm and does not affect his control of the ball.
Embiid (PHI) makes marginal contact with Hernangomez's (NOP) body as he attempts to establish position in the post and does not affect his ability to defend.
Green (PHI) makes incidental contact to Bledsoe's (NOP) arm after the release of his jump shot attempt.
Hernangomez (NOP) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Green (PHI) and slightly extends his arms, but does not dislodge him from his legally obtained position during the pick.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor of an out-of-bounds is overturned and a jump ball is administered at midcourt.
Curry (PHI) makes incidental contact with Bledsoe's (NOP) foot during the inbounds.
Bledsoe (NOP) makes clean contact to the ball after Harris (PHI) retrieves the inbounds pass.
Bledsoe (NOP) cleanly deflects the ball during Harris' (PHI) dribble.

With 10.4 seconds remaining, the ball is still not advanced into the frontcourt by the 76ers and an 8-second violation is correctly called.  On the previous possession, officials deem Green (PHI) to have control with 18.7 seconds remaining and a timeout is called with 14.8 seconds remaining and the ball was never advanced into the frontcourt.
Marshall (NOP) makes marginal contact with Harris's (PHI) body in the backcourt.
